Beenthere Vidhan Soudha Small Sling Bag (Khaki-03) Price: Rs.599

This is a trendy Sling Bag printed with a beautiful sketch of the Vidhan Soudha building of Bangalore. The bag carries little blips about the history of this monument. The neutral beige shade of the canvas fabric makes this bag an all occasion accessory. The canvas tape adds incredible style to the arty print of the bag. Use the bag for your day out in Namma Bengaluru. Gift it to friends who miss the city or to tourists and travelers to Bangalore. Use it as a souvenir for the city and show that you have beenthere.
